---
title: Double Indian-Spiced Pork & Bombay Veggie Fries with Apricot Glaze & Spring Onion Slaw
description: You can’t miss this tender pork loin, cooked in Mumbai spices and glazed in a sticky apricot sauce. Pair this with Bombay-flavoured veggie fries and a tangy slaw, and you’ve got a match made in food heaven!

